kydra (1.3.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Local .deb Package Management:
    * Treat local .deb files as their own "origin" in the package manager
    * Added "Local Files" filter option in the By Origin sidebar
    * Automatic detection of packages installed locally (not from repositories)
    * Local package directory indexing with file system watching
    * Support for multiple local package directories
    * Real-time scanning and indexing of .deb files in monitored directories
    * Integration with existing package filtering and search systems
    * Visual distinction for local packages with special icons and labels
  * Local Package Actions:
    * "Add Local Folder" toolbar button for adding package directories
    * "Install Local Package" toolbar button for installing individual .deb files
    * File dialog integration for easy directory and file selection
    * Safety checks before installation (dependency validation, architecture checks)
    * Progress indication during local package scanning
    * Automatic reload of package lists when local directories change
  * Enhanced Package Information:
    * Detailed metadata extraction from local .deb files
    * Display of package name, version, architecture, maintainer, and description
    * Dependency information parsing and validation
    * Conflict and compatibility checking
    * Integration with existing package details panels
  * New LocalPackageManager class for centralized local package handling
  * Singleton pattern for efficient resource management
  * File system watcher integration for real-time updates
  * Enhanced PackageProxyModel with local package filtering logic
  * Updated OriginFilter to include "Local Files" origin option
  * Comprehensive error handling and validation
  * Thread-safe package scanning and indexing
  * Integration with existing QApt backend infrastructure

 -- Jonathan Thomas <echidnaman@kubuntu.org>  Mon, 18 Nov 2025 19:30:00 +0100

