kydra (1.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Full Kirigami framework integration for modern Plasma-native UI
  * Kirigami.ApplicationWindow with global drawer navigation
  * Card-based layout with Kirigami.Card for package entries
  * Built-in animations and transitions using Kirigami behaviors
  * Adaptive layouts that work across different screen sizes
  * Standard KDE action buttons with proper icon theming
  * Enhanced Search & Filtering Experience:
    * Floating search bar with subtle drop shadow for modern visual appeal
    * Smart category filter chips (All, Applications, Development, Graphics, Multimedia, System)
    * Real-time search result highlighting with bold text for matched terms
    * Search results summary showing package count
    * Category-based filtering with intelligent package section mapping
    * Instant visual feedback during search operations
  * Footer toolbar with Kirigami.ActionToolBar
  * System theme integration with Kirigami.Theme.inherit
  * Context drawer for additional actions
  * Hover effects and smooth transitions throughout UI
  * Created KirigamiBackend bridge class for QML/C++ integration
  * PackageListModel for QML-accessible package data
  * Support for both traditional widget-based and Kirigami QML UI modes
  * Backend infrastructure for runtime UI mode switching
  * CMake integration for Kirigami framework dependencies
  * Added category filtering functionality with section-to-category mapping
  * Implemented search term highlighting in QML frontend

 -- Jonathan Thomas <echidnaman@kubuntu.org>  Mon, 18 Nov 2025 08:15:00 +0100

kydra (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add package-specific icon extraction from deb packages
  * Implement intelligent icon caching system with thread-safe access
  * Add fallback mechanism to generic deb icon when specific icons unavailable
  * Support icon extraction from installed desktop files
  * Search for icons in system icon themes and common directories
  * Add singleton-based PackageIconExtractor class for efficient management
  * Modernize PackageModel and PackageDelegate for dynamic icon loading
  * Implement comprehensive error handling for icon extraction failures

